仄平平平仄仄<br />\n平平仄仄仄平平(韻)<br />\n平平仄仄仄平平<br />\n仄仄平平仄仄平(韻)<br />\n二四六分明，得閒先執埋尾句第五字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"094a2d62eb201252ae5c7f1d7fb10c933a1389e2","tid":2366850,"uid":385899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5346a446d767122efcbb0155ccfbd1fcb9f6511f","tid":2366850,"uid":272485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T01:28:30.000Z","msg":"絕嶺雲深風嘯急，<br />\n殘英倦客足欲敝。<br />\n何嗟山道阻且長，<br />\n不見落絮艷勝霜？<br />\n<br />\n對仗同押韻都盡咗力，平仄無認真查考，聽落啱就算<br />\n求鍊字同格律建議"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T03:12:59.000Z","msg":"<strong>【依韻入詩】格律自動檢測索引教學系統</strong> <br />\n<a href=\"http://cls.lib.ntu.edu.tw/MakePoem/home.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcls.lib.ntu.edu.tw%2FMakePoem%2Fhome.htm&d=qXcR1A%2FTALq%2FhnoNE0cJVWWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=6dba21ab\" target=\"_blank\">http://cls.lib.ntu.edu.tw/MakePoem/home.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n樓主可以拎你首作品上去check下<br />\n七絕最少二四句末都要押韻<br />\n不過你睇嚟係三四句「長」「霜」押韻<br />\n依度有少少fail咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n平仄樓上有人講咗 唔多講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓主你加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f154b2bd246dd9bc97c8deaa33cc57ea03159a4","tid":2366850,"uid":42982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T03:14:25.000Z","msg":"幾個問題<br />\n<br />\n1. 你仲未準確分到平仄<br />\n2. 失粘<br />\n3. 七絕比較少三句都用韻"},{"pid":"7dc5acd281ff4a03c5000b355769750b80dda79c","tid":2366850,"uid":272485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d05de9b72b4ed0f5ee5a592bf4807e21d8489af","tid":2366850,"uid":272485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"133ef9605f7c6c1fe49a68539c3b8ed0362a7a3d","tid":2366850,"uid":42982,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5346a446d767122efcbb0155ccfbd1fcb9f6511f","tid":2366850,"uid":272485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T01:28:30.000Z","msg